pageProduct.name: Thursday Plantation Tea Tree Blemish Stick 7ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thursday Plantation Tea Tree Blemish Stick With Manuka Honey is dual action formula for acne-prone skin. Dries out blemishes & breakouts and helps improve the appearance of acne scars.

Thursday Plantation Tea Tree Blemish Stick is a dual action formula for acne-prone skin. Antibacterial Tea Tree Oil dries out pimples & breakouts, whilst Manuka Honey helps to improve the appearance of acne scars. The sponge-tip applicator is convenient & easy-to-use.

Product Claims: Product not tested on animals.

Size: 7mL

Dermatologist Tested?: Yes

Dermatologically Tested?: Yes

Non-Comedogenic?: Yes

Warnings

For external use only. Skin patch test prior to use. If sensitivity occurs discontinue use. Avoid contact with eyes. Do not apply to broken skin. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Water, Alcohol, Polysorbate 60, Glycerin, Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Leaf Oil, Carbomer, Honey Extract, Potassium Hydroxide, Mentha Viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Limonene, Linalool.

Directions

Apply to the appropriate areas as frequently as required.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30°C.

Storage Temperature: Blow 30°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle cardboard.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
